+ * sys_sched_getattr - similar to sched_getparam, but with sched_attr
+ * @pid: the pid in question.
+ * @uattr: structure containing the extended parameters.
+ * @size: sizeof(attr) for fwd/bwd comp.
+ * @flags: for future extension.
